                forgot to do this. Added team name to players in ManOfTheMatch.

  Version 2.5.2
  *************

  (23.01.00)  - Added RequestFile (by Torsten Poulin), Request Choice (by Joerg Riemer)
                and RequestString to archive for HTML and other scripts. Added more
                scripts - HTML_Played, Attendances, Bookings and TopScorers. Updated
                Referees and League Information scripts. Updated Player Information.
                Hopefully fixed bug where the 'Options' window went walkabout. Updated
                HTMLTemplates to work with Weekly scheduling. Updated ReformatSchedule
                to use the tools. Fixed bug where listviews were not sized correctly
